'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3141] on 7 December 2000 at 5:32:11 pm'!"Change Set:		keepingScoreDate:			7 December 2000Author:			Bob Arning- compress sounds when publishing SoundEventMorphs"!!SequentialSound methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'RAA 12/7/2000 17:24'!duration	"Answer the duration of this sound in seconds."	"7 dec 2000 - handle compressed sounds. better way??"	| dur |	dur _ 0.	sounds do: [:snd | dur _ dur + snd asSound duration].	^ dur! !!SoundEventMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 12/7/2000 17:10'!releaseCachedState	| codec newSound |	super releaseCachedState.	codec _ GSMCodec new.	newSound _ SequentialSound new.	sound sounds do: [ :aSound | 		newSound add: (			(aSound isKindOf: SampledSound) ifTrue: [				(codec compressSound: aSound)			] ifFalse: [				aSound			]		)	].	sound _ newSound.! !